at app'),('The visual combination of events and clock. It works for me.'),('Good !!!!'),('Good visual alternative to viewing your daily tasks.'),('Brilliant concept and great execution, very useful for keeping track of your day to day time management.'),('Best and simple app but , How do i activate 24 hour mode ?'),('Very good time keeping app. Great work developers.'),('Amazing... Love it'),('Loved it'),('YOU CAN GET THIS ON YOUR WATCH FACE TOO!!! Beautiful way of displaying time and events - my ADHD brain LOVES this. Nice customization of calendars, colors, and displays- don\'t be afraid to play with the settings. To get on your watch, install the smartphone app, then go to google play on your watch and select \"apps on my phone.\" From there you\'ll get the option to download Sectograph and then \"set watchface.\" Ps. Buy premium! One time payment and this dev deserves to get paid for this rad app.'),('Loveee It!'),(''),('it\'s so useful'),('Good'),('Really good app, made my day more organised.. Thanks to the developer...'),('I like its simplicity'),('by this app I can manage properly my time'),('The best'),('Loved it. Please add notification feature for events before they start (5mins or 10mins)'),('Nice apps, i\'ve using this for 2 years and still counting'),('Pwoli saanam myre '),('Great for visualizing time segments in a clean, organized format, pulling from your Google calendar(s). If you\'re more of a visual person and tend to overestimate or underestimate the time between tasks, or easily lose track of time, this may help.'),('Very Useful App To Schedule Your Day'),('So helpful!'),('I love the unique idea. I\'ve used this for my past two phones.'),('Great app!'),('I really like this app and it is definitely a very nice visual way to keep track of time. The one MAJOR issue I keep encountering though is that it does not seem to easily sync with my Google calendar, which is where I have all my daily tasks stored. Edit: after trying a few troubleshooting optio