gainst a wall. Please bring back the old Routines format ASAP.'),('incoherent jumble'),('what is the use of this app if it can not show notification with sound, also can not alert me when i m buzy in others chaos.'),('Interface is not really satisfactory'),('i have bad experience'),('complicated'),('Please tell me how to use the app'),('some thing is comming in front if screen and interepting. app is not runs in notification bar'),('Hi have been looking for a app which remind me each and every hour because I\'m a student and I need a that kind of app but in your application this feature is not available... '),('I missed my work today because of your stupid \"weak alarm\" method. This means I\'ve lost some money. Notification reliability should be of paramount importance. If something doesn\'t work 100%, remove it. Very disappointed. VERY! Edit: I didn\'t get any warning, nothing. If the other option is the recommended one (which I hate that it adds an alarm icon in the status bar. other apps work without doing this), it doesn\'t mean the other one IS NOT WORKING. Bad. I\'m forced to use the stock alarm for the first event in the morning to be sure, which is very inconvenient'),('Waste app.'),('I did not understand'),('This app is to complicated'),('Why this app requires so much of settings in one time.. 1)Like it should be in recent apps..2) If internet is off it doesn\'t works..3) Even though all the permissions to app is allowed in phone settings.. Than to it crashes.. It requires an immediate update with all the bugs fixed soon. Or people wouldn\'t even write a review.. They would uninstall the app and find better alternatives.'),('Worst app'),('It will ruin your plan, you are going to waste your time customizing it. Downloading this app will increase your screen time and degrade your efficiency.'),('Most of the things are paid'),('The new version is so complicated loved the old one it was simple and easy and quick to use it was perfect'),('I donk like this app a