date,it lost some features.Its not highlighting the current task in schedule pannel.Add this feature again in the next update... *EDIT : There is no \' now\' icon on the top bar.By the way,the method of highlighting the current task in schedule option before this update was better than the present way of highlighting. It\'s better to highlight the whole sentence instead of highlighting only the borders'),('thanks TimeTune been using ur app since 2018:  I achieved 1st place at local singing competition since you always remind me to practice  U always reminded me to work out at gym, now I\'m in a better shape  I made my clients happy because I arranged all my responsibilities fit their needs at a perfect time Thanks, will abosulely still using this when Alien invade the earth one day'),('I think this app will be amazing by seeing the reviews. I hope that it will be superb. I give 5 stars because it is like this app I was finding '),('Loving the app. It\'d be amazing if you could do calendar integrations with Outlook/ Gmail so that my work appointments could be reflected automatically.'),('Time to pick my life up and awaken my life.'),('Good app, Will there be a way to input a hex code for the color to the widget in a future update?'),('I think it\'s a great app...it has helped a lot...very efficient takes getting used to like any other app...I like this app very much'),(''),('Give us the damn todo list and app blocker all in one too '),('Just started and I finding this very easy operate. Thank you!'),('I love this app. I have been able to put my life together just by the free features of this app. I would always stress about having to do certain things everyday. I wouldn\'t do them because I had to remember to do them every day. Because of this app I don\'t have to remember to do them. I get reminded to do them and I do them happily. If I hadn\'t found this app, I don\'t know if I would have ever put my life together.'),('Nice app'),('If u want to be an organized person then u should have this app.... This was the app I was looking for.. It has many features... I can make a schedule for a particular day with a tag, title, description, and the main alarm....  I loved this app ..'),('What an app'),('Great App! Absolutely love using it to plan out my day! Thank you!'),('Excellent'),('It works perfectly, for us the best app'),('I\'ve only just started using this app, but it seems to be exactly what I was looking for. It allows you to create customised event types, programme start and end times for events, set repeating events. It\'s simple, but not lacking in features. One suggestion I have is the ability to see a weekly view of the schedule.'),('It is quite good for managing your schedule and having your schedule written down somewhere instead of it being in your head. You could definitely use it for your professional life. I only use it for personal.'),('It\'s amazing. I like the way it is so don\'t try anything odd. Soon I will try the premium'),('Best of its kind .'),('i like this app. it would be nice if it highlights what part of your routine you are in.'),('Nice, exactly what I needed'),('Easy to use app for making a schedule. I like it very much.'),('This app is very helpful.... It really helps me to optimize my time and do things schedule-wise..... awesome and productive app.....thanks to developers......'),('Awesome! Helps keep track of all your day to day activities and it can sync to your calendar\'s!'),('Finally found what I\'m looking for. Great app!'),('Make for IOS Please'),('I just came back from a year or more of not using the app (I didn\'t really have a routine) and I\'ve gotta say the design changes are amazing. It\'s visually easier to navigate and edit. The ideas in blocks are great. Can\'t wait to see you implement more things to do with overlaps and such.'),('This app is freaking phenomenal! Instead of having a billion alarms in my phone that I have to go over all the time, I can just set up schedules and go