h you could download it for your PC as well.'),('It\'s cool'),('I just downloaded this.  The free version was definitely useful but I went ahead and got the paid version because I wanted to use the repetitive tasks and weekly planner as well.  I definitely think this will be worth the purchase.'),('I really like this app and ised to love it until there was an update that was stopping me from using it without upgrading. If i had to pay a one time purchase thats one thing but an annual fee?? Give me a break. $5 for a planner app is reasonable if you use it all of the time but not every year. Yall are greedy.'),('This app is great! But i have some suggestions that would even better improve the quality of using the app. for example, something like being able to edit the tasks widgets to show \'due soon\' instead of just tasks for that day for even better planning.'),('Great app!    Help,  I unfortunately forgot my password (I was very sure it\'s correct but I\'m not sure why it says it\'s wrong). Is there anything that can be done about it?'),('This is a great planner app. Only thing missing is the ability to rotate into portrait or even rotate 180 degrees.'),('The app was working fine until I removed Google Now. Now the widgets will not show on home page.'),('planned not bad'),('This is the app which I use for almost a year. There is one issue I have faced recently. Namely, some tasks and events do not synchronize on multiple devices where I installed the app. I\'m using this app on my Android smartphone, as well as on iPad. I would be very pleased if you fix it.'),('Greatly improved comment from me.  MUCH better than a year ago.  Most updated lead to improvement.  Wish the \' want an annual subscription.'),('It\'s '),('Almost all the functionality of the Franklin Planner. This is a great app!'),('The calendar reminders can be very shotty but the overall app is very useful'),('This is a simple app, that gives me the capability of creating a to-do list, set event on my 